        <p>So it is no surprise to see that beadwork designs which emphasize four-fold symmetry--two orthogonal axes--are common in these cultures.</p>
        <p>In addition to the Cartesian grid, Indigenous beadworkers developed their own concept of algorithms: the sequence of instructions that produce bead patterns. The software in this unit will allow you to experiment with re-discovering these heritage algorithms, and inventing your own.</p>
